ock the specified email addresses from being able to sign up or sign in to your site. To block an entire domain, use something like `*@domain.com`.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This option lets you specify blacklist of words to prevent anyone from signing up with such a word as their username.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Emails'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Email sender options'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'How the sender appears in outgoing Ultimate Member emails.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Admin Email Address'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'e.g. admin@companyname.com.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'e.g. Site Name.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Email template'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Section to customize email templates settings.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Content type'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable HTML for Emails'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'If you plan use emails with HTML, please make sure that this option is enabled. Otherwise, HTML will be displayed as plain text.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user profile template and size. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more about custom profile template creation</a>.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This will be the default template to output profile.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The maximum width this shortcode can take from the page width.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The maximum width of the profile area inside profile (below profile header).'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the profile photo component on the user profile.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Profile Photo Upload'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the profile photo uploader.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The global default of profile photo size. This can be overridden by individual form settings.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the profile cover photos.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The global default width of cover photo size. This can be overridden by individual form settings.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Choose global ratio for cover photos of profiles.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Header'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user profile header component.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show icons in Profile Header Meta'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Display field icons for related user meta fields in header or not.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Display name in profile header'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the user name on profile header.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Social links in profile header'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the social links on profile header.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'User description in profile header'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show user description in profile header'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the user description on profile header.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'HTML support for user description'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off to enable/disable support for HTML tags on user description.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Buttons & Fields'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user profile buttons and fields layout.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The text that is used for updating profile button.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show Profile Secondary Button'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the secondary button display in the form.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The text that is used for cancelling update profile button.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This is applicable for edit mode only.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Custom message on empty profile'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the custom message that appears when the profile is empty.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Custom message emoticon'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the emoticon (sad face) that appears above the message.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user profiles menus on your site.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user registration template and size.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This will be the default template to output registration.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The shortcode is centered by default unless you specify otherwise here.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user registration buttons and fields layout.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The text that is used for primary button text.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show Registration Secondary Button'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The text that is used for the secondary button text.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'You can replace default link for this button by entering custom URL.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This controls the display of field icons in the registration form.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user login template and size.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This will be the default template to output login.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section allows you to customize the user login buttons and fields layout.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show Login Secondary Button'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show Login Forgot Password Link'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Switch on/off the forgot password link in login form.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'"Remember Me" checkbox'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Show "Remember Me" checkbox'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This controls the display of field icons in the login form.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Advanced settings section is designed to help you fine-tune your website or add extra features. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more about advanced settings section</a>.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Required fields\' asterisk'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Cache User Profile'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Disable user data cache'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable flushing data'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Each time we release an update, you\'ll find a list of changes made to the template files. <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Learn more about overriding templates</a>.<br />You can easily check the status of the latest templates to see if they are up-to-date or need updating. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">Learn more about fixing outdated templates</a>.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Features'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Start using new features that are being progressively rolled out to improve the users management experience.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Gutenberg Blocks'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Experimental features'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'These features are either experimental or incomplete, enable them at your own risk!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Design scheme'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable new UI (for developers only)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Check this box if you would like to enable new UI.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable new Form Builder (for developers only)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Check this box if you would like to enable new Form Builder.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Legacy fonticons'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable legacy fonticons'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Check this box if you would like to enable legacy Ultimate Member fonticons used outdated versions of FontAwesome and Ionicons libraries.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Legacy features'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'These features are related to the legacy logic or functionality. Please enable them only for the backward compatibility.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Restriction content pre-queries'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Disable pre-queries for restriction content logic'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Please enable this option only in the cases when you have big or unnecessary queries on your site with active restriction logic. If you want to exclude posts only from the results queries instead of pre_get_posts and fully-hidden post logic also please enable this option. It activates the restriction content logic until 2.2.x version without latest security enhancements.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Developers'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This section is designed to modify settings that are tailored for developers. If you are not a developer, please be cautious when changing these settings.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Allowed Choice Callbacks (Enter one PHP function per line)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This option lets you specify the choice callback functions to prevent anyone from using 3rd-party functions that may put your site at risk.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'REST API Version'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'This controls the REST API version, we recommend to use the last version.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Redirect'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Allows to manage redirect settings.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Allow external link redirect confirm'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable JS.confirm for external links'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Using JS.confirm alert when you go to an external link.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'System info'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Action Scheduler'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Enable Action Scheduler'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'Check this box if you want to use the Ultimate Member action scheduler. By enabling it, certain tasks like sending system emails will be scheduled to run at optimal times, which can help reduce the load on your server'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]],'The <strong>"Membership - Anyone can register"</strong> option on the general settings <a href="%s">page</a> is enabled. This means users can register via the standard WordPress wp-login.php page. If you do not want users to be able to register via this page and only register via the Ultimate Member registration form, you should deactivate this option. You can dismiss this notice if you wish to keep the wp-login.php registration page open.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['ultimate-member',1]]]];
